{"tid":2011353,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【玩家叫苦】受「小粉紅」舉報　PSN 中國地區暫時下架　","createTime":"2020-05-11T02:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T04:13:54.000Z","uid":104138,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6c84e850f966d4d1fa91861aa8e1aca28cadb23a","tid":2011353,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T02:45:50.000Z","msg":"中國大陸地區用戶因為國家的政策，所有遊戲都會經過嚴格的審查，確定沒有「色情、暴力、敏感內容」才會開放給國民購買，亦有網絡限制，用戶不能翻牆到其它網絡地區。不過只要外國地區有一些「潛在攻擊中國人」的言論或內容，都會有「愛國小粉紅」的網民翻牆攻擊，或舉報涉嫌違反中國網絡使用守則的事項，近日中國地區的 PlayStation 官方，亦因為「愛國小粉紅」的舉報而需要「更新」，導致大量中國大錄用戶不滿。<br />\n<br />\n有愛國小粉紅中國網友名為「森里螢四」，檢舉Sony PlayStation 的「SIE」服務「PlayStation Network」（PSN）中國國行版，聲稱服務存有漏洞，可以讓國內的用戶，連線到包括香港地區的未經審核商店，購買並下載遊戲，可以下載《鐵血戰士》《GTA V》等「鼓吹暴力色情、血腥、販賣毒品等，嚴重危害廣大青少年身心健康的遊戲作品。」而的確成功讓 PSN 自中國下架。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/05/10/psn-chian-area-block-in-may-10/s__32776211/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2020%2F05%2F10%2Fpsn-chian-area-block-in-may-10%2Fs__32776211%2F&h=e909b95e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國地區的 PlayStation 表示，中國商店暫停服務通知，由於 PlayStation 中國商店系統安全升級的原因，中國地區商店將於5月10日早上七時起暫停服務，對於用戶造成的不便我們深感抱歉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/05/10/psn-chian-area-block-in-may-10/s__32776213/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2020%2F05%2F10%2Fpsn-chian-area-block-in-may-10%2Fs__32776213%2F&h=93c9ea3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/05/10/psn-chian-area-block-in-may-10/s__32776216/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2020%2F05%2F10%2Fpsn-chian-area-block-in-may-10%2Fs__32776216%2F&h=5b29654e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/05/10/psn-chian-area-block-in-may-10/s__32776215/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2020%2F05%2F10%2Fpsn-chian-area-block-in-may-10%2Fs__32776215%2F&h=1c891f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2020/05/10/psn-chian-area-block-in-may-10/s__32776217/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2020%2F05%2F10%2Fpsn-chian-area-block-in-may-10%2Fs__32776217%2F&h=66494cfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此舉導致到大量中國地區玩家指責舉報事件的愛國小粉紅，表示：「你母親節幹這種事會失去媽的」，大量玩家檢舉那位小粉紅，最後導致該名「森里螢四」網友舉報成為無效帳戶，但一切已經太遲"},{"pid":"22975274d94394a9c719163f72ef0e95a36a9b56","tid":2011353,"uid":211062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T02:48:13.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ca3356ccf881f76bb07ea08c725be4e4857f70","tid":2011353,"uid":211062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T02:48:49.000Z","msg":"不推文"},{"pid":"1f17e4f1fb7c0ab123e49a2b9b3c7e5eed3e2d82","tid":2011353,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T02:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5ea58722c784ba2cf4600e1c3aee0a4df422f3","tid":2011353,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T03:25:07.000Z","msg":"「你母親節幹這種事會失去媽的」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8666d283d16e05a7a54ff1a5db1685850c4981","tid":2011353,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T03:26:42.000Z","msg":"想買ps4,"},{"pid":"faa72de94df18d5d81d463464ba95ef9372318b3","tid":2011353,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T03:43:49.000Z","msg":"🥺🥺🥺"},{"pid":"bb1562d143710dd0bbd1d0c1e471a051d90ba8e0","tid":2011353,"uid":357030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T03:51:39.000Z","msg":"你還有黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4408d2bd357badb0db546890514e367e2f63fd26","tid":2011353,"uid":321147,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:13:54.000Z","msg":"舉報嗰個品蔥用戶嚟，今次係加速成功"}]}